{"tid":1805162,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚首爾弘大人鏈嘅港韓手足們，多謝你地！","createTime":"2019-12-31T12:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T14:38:39.000Z","uid":60936,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aa23149349a058c1c30f5fa47d403e4c7ccb63d6","tid":1805162,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"零下7度，一條長長嘅人鏈係弘大築起，<br />\n係寒風中嗌口號，中英韓都嗌勻晒，又拎住文宣海報俾途人睇，屌，好撚感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚凍㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30scisS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30scisS.jpg&h=20e7bf2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左2枝熱嘅蜂蜜紅參飲品俾拎旗同播片嘅手足飲，希望你地保重身體，唔好冷親<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">太多人我買唔晒俾咁多個sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZcPkGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZcPkGW.jpg&h=543840b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國線好重要㗎，好多活動成日搞，<br />\n好似黎緊1月4到5號就有個文宣展，會去韓國嘅大家可以去睇，韓國線真係絕對不可忽視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTFJqbn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTFJqbn.jpg&h=fd3f1278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">광복홍콩 시대혁명</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccfba6e7a33ae30927e11f8ed191c0cc6a30718","tid":1805162,"uid":270237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RHxvPDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRHxvPDs.jpg&h=5831d4a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b086c358bb54770564b86aaeae72b2abe1dd07c","tid":1805162,"uid":17430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74eca0897eb47c0c96873aadc276b0f419890a73","tid":1805162,"uid":334523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4021736d786804bfbcb0ebd4491b56ac926c7a9c","tid":1805162,"uid":314270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"仲係唔係度,趕緊黎"},{"pid":"d8d076557ebf8e6cd55d54d8a94564225c9f5e7b","tid":1805162,"uid":267310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4021736d786804bfbcb0ebd4491b56ac926c7a9c","tid":1805162,"uid":314270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"仲係唔係度,趕緊黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"佢地話等陣會去普信閣倒數"},{"pid":"87699fb9f01b1192db123f46cb1b1c76222ee7b4","tid":1805162,"uid":267310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4021736d786804bfbcb0ebd4491b56ac926c7a9c","tid":1805162,"uid":314270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"仲係唔係度,趕緊黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"9點完咗"},{"pid":"8fe2177dbc46e906dec740057cfde2a193ecd988","tid":1805162,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8d076557ebf8e6cd55d54d8a94564225c9f5e7b","tid":1805162,"uid":267310,"li